    "career": "In a work-related reading, the Tower can signify a significant organisational change or event\nthat has a substantial impact on you personally. Your company may go through a crisis or\ndownsizing its operations and cutting costs, putting your job under threat. This is not an\nindicator that you need to",
    "relationships": "If you are in search of love, you may have a defining moment that forces you to revise your\napproach to finding the right relationship. An unexpected change of events may push you\nto question your current path and compel you in a new direction. You may realise you have\nbeen chasing after the wrong p",
    "spirituality": "Your faith will be put to the test. The Tower indicates that a significant change will challenge\nyour fundamental belief system. This is also a ‘make or break’ moment for you on a spiritual\nlevel, which will test how committed you are to your spiritual development. It may reflect a\nspiritual awakeni",
    "journaling": " What radical shifts and unexpected changes are you experiencing right now? What is the\nblessing in disguise?\n What structures and belief systems do you realise no longer hold true for you? What is\nemerging instead?\n How can you be a catalyst for change? How can you challenge the status quo and c"
