    "career": "In a work or business-related reading, the Moon suggests that all is not as it seems. There\nmay be shady business dealings going on that you are not aware of or are choosing to ignore.\nThere may be fraudulent activities or hidden agendas unravelling your work or business\nsuccess. Do not take things ",
    "relationships": "In a relationship reading, the Moon card can suggest illusions and deception. Don’t take\nthings on face value – dig a little deeper to see what’s going on underneath the surface. If\nsomething seems ‘off’, then it probably is. Be careful that you do not get swept up in the\nexcitement for finding love",
    "spirituality": "The Moon shows that you are in tune with your intuition and may receive psychic messages\nand ‘downloads’ through meditation, self-hypnosis, or your dreams. You may also be more\nopen to receiving a psychic reading to connect you to your intuition.\nGiven the strong association with the moon, align you",
    "journaling": " What are your deepest fears and anxieties?\n What is uncertain at this time?\n How can you connect with your intuition?"
