    "spirituality": "Judgement is a positive card to see in a spiritual reading. It reflects a moment of spiritual\nawakening, where your connection with your soul and the Universe becomes crystal clear,\nand you know what you need to do to reach enlightenment.\nYou are receptive to spiritual messages and may find solace i",
