    "spirituality": "On a spiritual level, the World sees you accepting and loving yourself for who you are and\nletting go of your harmful illusions about yourself and what you can or cannot accomplish.\nThe World also indicates a sense of wholeness and knowing your place within the world\nand how you can make a positive ",
