    "meaning_up": "With the Ace of Cups, Divine love and compassion are pouring through you. You are a vessel\nfor deep, spiritual love from the Universe, and you can’t help but let that love flow through\nyou and into the world. You receive love, you give love, you ARE love. Your heart overflows.\nNow is the perfect time for you to open your heart and experience the rich flow of emotion\navailable to you right now. You are more receptive to creative opportunities, loving\nconnections, and deep compassion for other living beings. As with all Aces in the Tarot,\nthis card comes as an invitation. Will you take it? Will ",
