    "career": "In a career-related reading, the Ace of Cups suggests you are experiencing pure joy and\nemotional fulfilment in your job. You can fully and authentically express yourself, and tap\ninto the ‘flow’ when you’re hard at work.\n\nIn a financial reading, the Ace of Cups can be a sign of contentment and happ",
    "relationships": "If you are single, then the Ace of Cups is a wonderful card to see in a reading! It suggests the\nstart of a new relationship filled with love and happiness. It has the potential to turn into\nsomething more substantial and long-term – if you open your heart and allow yourself to\n‘feel the feels’.\nIf ",
    "spirituality": "The Ace of Cups is a profoundly spiritual card that signifies the connection between your\nsubconscious and inner voice and the power to manifest new beginnings. You will perceive\nthe deep connection with your spirit and soul and the Universe, and you are open to new\nways to create spiritual transfor",
    "journaling": " How can I express myself creatively?\n How can I express myself emotionally?\n How does love flow through me?"
