    "career": "In a work-related reading, the Five of Cups acknowledges that you may have found yourself\nin a position you regret, one where you have let others down or made mistakes. Instead\nof dwelling on it, take responsibility for the choices you made, learn from your mistakes,\nthen move on. Look for new oppor",
    "relationships": "If you are looking for love, you may find yourself temporarily disappointed as someone with\na lot of promise and potential is not quite who you thought they were (or they are not as\ninterested in the relationship as you hoped). You may need to reassess your expectations\nif this becomes a pattern and",
    "spirituality": "On a spiritual level, the Five of Cups invites you to forgive and move on. Not only are you\nbeing asked to forgive others, but you are also being asked to forgive yourself. Through\nself-acceptance and the understanding that you are trying to do your best, you can release\nyourself of any pain associa",
