    "career": "In a work-related reading, the Seven of Cups suggests that you have a variety of choices\navailable to you. You may have job offers, business opportunities or projects you can work\non. Before you invest your time and energy, do your research and know what you are signing\nup for – if an offer seems to",
    "relationships": "If you are looking for love, the Seven of Cups indicates that you have potential suitors trying to\nwin you over. Not all will be the people they say they are, so be specific about what you want\nin a relationship, weigh your choices thoughtfully and be honest with everyone involved\n(including yoursel",
    "spirituality": "In a spiritual reading, the Seven of Cups invites you to see the world through optimistic eyes.\nLook for the blessings in disguise and cue in to the opportunities available to you. Stay in\nalignment with your personal values and the most authentic part of yourself so you can\nconsciously pick which o",
