    "meaning_up": "When the Eight of Cups shows up in a Tarot reading, you may feel compelled to walk away from\na disappointing situation. It could mean turning your back on an unfulfilling relationship,\njob, career path, living arrangement or creative project that was once a source of great\nhappiness to you but now only brings you pain. You have invested yourself emotionally but,\ndespite your best efforts, are disappointed; it hasn’t turned out the way you had expected it\nto, and you realise that you are no longer getting anything out of this situation. Now, the only\nchoice is to put it behind you and move on w",
