    "career": "In a work-related reading, the Eight of Cups often arrives when your current job or career\npath is no longer serving you, and you are ready to move on. You may feel bored, burnt-out\nor under-appreciated. It may be time to look for a job elsewhere or consider a career change.\nIt may be disruptive, bu",
    "relationships": "If you are looking for love, the Eight of Cups suggests that you may prefer a ‘time out’ and\navoid new relationships at this stage. It is more important to connect with yourself and\nheal from any past disappointments. You know you are not ready to give yourself to a new\nrelationship and would not be",
    "spirituality": "The Eight of Cups suggests that you are undertaking a spiritual journey or quest to leave\nbehind your emotional and physical attachments and get to the core of your inner being. You\nmight consider a vision quest, social media sabbatical, or a vegan lifestyle, leaving behind\nany unhealthy attachments",
