    "relationships": "Overall, the Nine of Cups is an excellent omen for your love life and relationships as it shows\nemotional fulfilment, contentment and satisfaction.\nIf you are looking for love, the Nine of Cups suggests that you will meet some great people.\nGet out, mingle, strike up conversations with the people yo",
