    "relationships": "If you are looking for love, the Ace of Pentacles points to a new opportunity on the horizon. The\nsuit of Pentacles suggests the opening may present itself to you in a work context, perhaps by\nmeeting someone through work or with similar career interests as you. This card also speaks\nto manifestatio",
    "spirituality": "While the Ace of Pentacles has a strong connection to the material realm, this card can also\nreflect abundance and wealth in a spiritual sense. If you radiate positive energy into the\nUniverse, it will come back to you. Consider, too, how you can manifest your spiritual goals\nby undertaking real act",
