    "relationships": "If you are looking for love, you may find that work or other commitments are taking over your\nlife, leaving little time or energy to invest in a new relationship. Use the time you do have\nwisely! Be clear on where your priorities lie. If you are keen to find a partner, then you may\nneed to stop othe",
    "spirituality": "Are you so consumed in the day-to-day affairs that you have little time for your spiritual\ndevelopment? The Two of Pentacles says yes. Focusing on your spirituality takes time and\nspace, but you must create and prioritise these resources. By investing time in meditation\nand an inward focus, you will",
