    "career": "In a career reading, the Nine of Swords sees you getting very worked up over a particular\nissue at work, causing yourself great anxiety and stress. Remember that it is just a job. Even if\nyou have made a significant mistake, the fallout will soon be forgotten, and you will see that\nthings are not as",
    "relationships": "If you are looking for love, you may be feeling anxious that you have not found someone yet.\nUnfortunately, this fear can create a downward spiral. As you worry more and more about\nnot finding someone, you spend more of your time worrying than you do looking for love.\nBreak that cycle! Use positive ",
    "spirituality": "In a spiritual reading, the Nine of Swords reflects that you have hit one of your darkest\nmoments and are feeling stressed and anxious about life. Instead of continuing down this\npath of worry and inner torment, it is time to change the cycle and bring greater positivity\nand faith into your life. No",
    "journaling": " What is troubling me? Is it real or perceived?\n How are my negative thoughts affecting my day-to-day experience?\n How can I look at my circumstances from a different, more positive perspective?"
