    "career": "The Knight of Swords notes that you are actively pursuing your goals, meeting your targets\nand pushing your projects and tasks forward with high energy and pace. You are not willing\nto let anyone or anything stand in your way and will assertively stand up to anyone who tries\nto oppose you. You skilf",
